{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Up until now, our communication with machines"},{"time":3000,"text":"has always been limited"},{"time":5000,"text":"to conscious and direct forms."},{"time":7000,"text":"Whether it's something simple"},{"time":9000,"text":"like turning on the lights with a switch,"},{"time":11000,"text":"or even as complex as programming robotics,"},{"time":14000,"text":"we have always had to give a command to a machine,"},{"time":17000,"text":"or even a series of commands,"},{"time":19000,"text":"in order for it to do something for us."},{"time":22000,"text":"Communication between people, on the other hand,"},{"time":24000,"text":"is far more complex and a lot more interesting"},{"time":27000,"text":"because we take into account"},{"time":29000,"text":"so much more than what is explicitly expressed."},{"time":32000,"text":"We observe facial expressions, body language,"},{"time":35000,"text":"and we can intuit feelings and emotions"},{"time":37000,"text":"from our dialogue with one another."},{"time":40000,"text":"This actually forms a large part"},{"time":42000,"text":"of our decision-making process."},{"time":44000,"text":"Our vision is to introduce"},{"time":46000,"text":"this whole new realm of human interaction"},{"time":49000,"text":"into human-computer interaction"},{"time":51000,"text":"so that computers can understand"},{"time":53000,"text":"not only what you direct it to do,"},{"time":55000,"text":"but it can also respond"},{"time":57000,"text":"to your facial expressions"},{"time":59000,"text":"and emotional experiences."},{"time":61000,"text":"And what better way to do this"},{"time":63000,"text":"than by interpreting the signals"},{"time":65000,"text":"naturally produced by our brain,"},{"time":67000,"text":"our center for control and experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70000,"text":"Well, it sounds like a pretty good idea,"},{"time":72000,"text":"but this task, as Bruno mentioned,"},{"time":74000,"text":"isn't an easy one for two main reasons:"},{"time":77000,"text":"First, the detection algorithms."},{"time":80000,"text":"Our brain is made up of"},{"time":82000,"text":"billions of active neurons,"},{"time":84000,"text":"around 170,000 km"},{"time":87000,"text":"of combined axon length."},{"time":89000,"text":"When these neurons interact,"},{"time":91000,"text":"the chemical reaction emits an electrical impulse,"},{"time":93000,"text":"which can be measured."},{"time":95000,"text":"The majority of our functional brain"},{"time":98000,"text":"is distributed over"},{"time":100000,"text":"the outer surface layer of the brain,"},{"time":102000,"text":"and to increase the area that's available for mental capacity,"},{"time":105000,"text":"the brain surface is highly folded."},{"time":108000,"text":"Now this cortical folding"},{"time":110000,"text":"presents a significant challenge"},{"time":112000,"text":"for interpreting surface electrical impulses."},{"time":115000,"text":"Each individual's cortex"},{"time":117000,"text":"is folded differently,"},{"time":119000,"text":"very much like a fingerprint."},{"time":121000,"text":"So even though a signal"},{"time":123000,"text":"may come from the same functional part of the brain,"},{"time":126000,"text":"by the time the structure has been folded,"},{"time":128000,"text":"its physical location"},{"time":130000,"text":"is very different between individuals,"},{"time":132000,"text":"even identical twins."},{"time":135000,"text":"There is no longer any consistency"},{"time":137000,"text":"in the surface signals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"Our breakthrough was to create an algorithm"},{"time":141000,"text":"that unfolds the cortex,"},{"time":143000,"text":"so that we can map the signals"},{"time":145000,"text":"closer to its source,"},{"time":147000,"text":"and therefore making it capable of working across a mass population."},{"time":151000,"text":"The second challenge"},{"time":153000,"text":"is the actual device for observing brainwaves."},{"time":156000,"text":"EEG measurements typically involve"},{"time":158000,"text":"a hairnet with an array of sensors,"},{"time":161000,"text":"like the one that you can see here in the photo."},{"time":164000,"text":"A technician will put the electrodes"},{"time":166000,"text":"onto the scalp"},{"time":168000,"text":"using a conductive gel or paste"},{"time":170000,"text":"and usually after a procedure of preparing the scalp"},{"time":173000,"text":"by light abrasion."},{"time":175000,"text":"Now this is quite time consuming"},{"time":177000,"text":"and isn't the most comfortable process."},{"time":179000,"text":"And on top of that, these systems"},{"time":181000,"text":"actually cost in the tens of thousands of dollars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"So with that, I'd like to invite onstage"},{"time":188000,"text":"Evan Grant, who is one of last year's speakers,"},{"time":190000,"text":"who's kindly agreed"},{"time":192000,"text":"to help me to demonstrate"},{"time":194000,"text":"what we've been able to develop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"So the device that you see"},{"time":204000,"text":"is a 14-channel, high-fidelity"},{"time":206000,"text":"EEG acquisition system."},{"time":208000,"text":"It doesn't require any scalp preparation,"},{"time":211000,"text":"no conductive gel or paste."},{"time":213000,"text":"It only takes a few minutes to put on"},{"time":216000,"text":"and for the signals to settle."},{"time":218000,"text":"It's also wireless,"},{"time":220000,"text":"so it gives you the freedom to move around."},{"time":223000,"text":"And compared to the tens of thousands of dollars"},{"time":226000,"text":"for a traditional EEG system,"},{"time":229000,"text":"this headset only costs"},{"time":231000,"text":"a few hundred dollars."},{"time":233000,"text":"Now on to the detection algorithms."},{"time":236000,"text":"So facial expressions --"},{"time":238000,"text":"as I mentioned before in emotional experiences --"},{"time":240000,"text":"are actually designed to work out of the box"},{"time":242000,"text":"with some sensitivity adjustments"},{"time":244000,"text":"available for personalization."},{"time":247000,"text":"But with the limited time we have available,"},{"time":249000,"text":"I'd like to show you the cognitive suite,"},{"time":251000,"text":"which is the ability for you"},{"time":253000,"text":"to basically move virtual objects with your mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"Now, Evan is new to this system,"},{"time":259000,"text":"so what we have to do first"},{"time":261000,"text":"is create a new profile for him."},{"time":263000,"text":"He's obviously not Joanne -- so we'll \"add user.\""},{"time":266000,"text":"Evan. Okay."},{"time":268000,"text":"So the first thing we need to do with the cognitive suite"},{"time":271000,"text":"is to start with training"},{"time":273000,"text":"a neutral signal."},{"time":275000,"text":"With neutral, there's nothing in particular"},{"time":277000,"text":"that Evan needs to do."},{"time":279000,"text":"He just hangs out. He's relaxed."},{"time":281000,"text":"And the idea is to establish a baseline"},{"time":283000,"text":"or normal state for his brain,"},{"time":285000,"text":"because every brain is different."},{"time":287000,"text":"It takes eight seconds to do this,"},{"time":289000,"text":"and now that that's done,"},{"time":291000,"text":"we can choose a movement-based action."},{"time":293000,"text":"So Evan, choose something"},{"time":295000,"text":"that you can visualize clearly in your mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"Evan Grant: Let's do \"pull.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"Tan Le: Okay, so let's choose \"pull.\""},{"time":301000,"text":"So the idea here now"},{"time":303000,"text":"is that Evan needs to"},{"time":305000,"text":"imagine the object coming forward"},{"time":307000,"text":"into the screen,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and there's a progress bar that will scroll across the screen"},{"time":312000,"text":"while he's doing that."},{"time":314000,"text":"The first time, nothing will happen,"},{"time":316000,"text":"because the system has no idea how he thinks about \"pull.\""},{"time":319000,"text":"But maintain that thought"},{"time":321000,"text":"for the entire duration of the eight seconds."},{"time":323000,"text":"So: one, two, three, go."},{"time":334000,"text":"Okay."},{"time":336000,"text":"So once we accept this,"},{"time":338000,"text":"the cube is live."},{"time":340000,"text":"So let's see if Evan"},{"time":342000,"text":"can actually try and imagine pulling."},{"time":345000,"text":"Ah, good job!"},{"time":347000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":350000,"text":"That's really amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"So we have a little bit of time available,"},{"time":358000,"text":"so I'm going to ask Evan"},{"time":360000,"text":"to do a really difficult task."},{"time":362000,"text":"And this one is difficult"},{"time":364000,"text":"because it's all about being able to visualize something"},{"time":367000,"text":"that doesn't exist in our physical world."},{"time":369000,"text":"This is \"disappear.\""},{"time":371000,"text":"So what you want to do -- at least with movement-based actions,"},{"time":373000,"text":"we do that all the time, so you can visualize it."},{"time":376000,"text":"But with \"disappear,\" there's really no analogies --"},{"time":378000,"text":"so Evan, what you want to do here"},{"time":380000,"text":"is to imagine the cube slowly fading out, okay."},{"time":383000,"text":"Same sort of drill. So: one, two, three, go."},{"time":395000,"text":"Okay. Let's try that."},{"time":398000,"text":"Oh, my goodness. He's just too good."},{"time":402000,"text":"Let's try that again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"EG: Losing concentration."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"TL: But we can see that it actually works,"},{"time":415000,"text":"even though you can only hold it"},{"time":417000,"text":"for a little bit of time."},{"time":419000,"text":"As I said, it's a very difficult process"},{"time":422000,"text":"to imagine this."},{"time":424000,"text":"And the great thing about it is that"},{"time":426000,"text":"we've only given the software one instance"},{"time":428000,"text":"of how he thinks about \"disappear.\""},{"time":431000,"text":"As there is a machine learning algorithm in this --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":434000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":440000,"text":"Good job. Good job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"Thank you, Evan, you're a wonderful, wonderful"},{"time":448000,"text":"example of the technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451000,"text":"So, as you can see, before,"},{"time":453000,"text":"there is a leveling system built into this software"},{"time":456000,"text":"so that as Evan, or any user,"},{"time":458000,"text":"becomes more familiar with the system,"},{"time":460000,"text":"they can continue to add more and more detections,"},{"time":463000,"text":"so that the system begins to differentiate"},{"time":465000,"text":"between different distinct thoughts."},{"time":469000,"text":"And once you've trained up the detections,"},{"time":471000,"text":"these thoughts can be assigned or mapped"},{"time":473000,"text":"to any computing platform,"},{"time":475000,"text":"application or device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"So I'd like to show you a few examples,"},{"time":479000,"text":"because there are many possible applications"},{"time":481000,"text":"for this new interface."},{"time":484000,"text":"In games and virtual worlds, for example,"},{"time":486000,"text":"your facial expressions"},{"time":488000,"text":"can naturally and intuitively be used"},{"time":490000,"text":"to control an avatar or virtual character."},{"time":494000,"text":"Obviously, you can experience the fantasy of magic"},{"time":496000,"text":"and control the world with your mind."},{"time":501000,"text":"And also, colors, lighting,"},{"time":504000,"text":"sound and effects"},{"time":506000,"text":"can dynamically respond to your emotional state"},{"time":508000,"text":"to heighten the experience that you're having, in real time."},{"time":512000,"text":"And moving on to some applications"},{"time":514000,"text":"developed by developers and researchers around the world,"},{"time":517000,"text":"with robots and simple machines, for example --"},{"time":520000,"text":"in this case, flying a toy helicopter"},{"time":522000,"text":"simply by thinking \"lift\" with your mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525000,"text":"The technology can also be applied"},{"time":527000,"text":"to real world applications --"},{"time":529000,"text":"in this example, a smart home."},{"time":531000,"text":"You know, from the user interface of the control system"},{"time":534000,"text":"to opening curtains"},{"time":536000,"text":"or closing curtains."},{"time":547000,"text":"And of course, also to the lighting --"},{"time":550000,"text":"turning them on"},{"time":553000,"text":"or off."},{"time":555000,"text":"And finally,"},{"time":557000,"text":"to real life-changing applications,"},{"time":559000,"text":"such as being able to control an electric wheelchair."},{"time":562000,"text":"In this example,"},{"time":564000,"text":"facial expressions are mapped to the movement commands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":567000,"text":"Man: Now blink right to go right."},{"time":575000,"text":"Now blink left to turn back left."},{"time":587000,"text":"Now smile to go straight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"TL: We really -- Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":600000,"text":"We are really only scratching the surface of what is possible today,"},{"time":603000,"text":"and with the community's input,"},{"time":605000,"text":"and also with the involvement of developers"},{"time":607000,"text":"and researchers from around the world,"},{"time":610000,"text":"we hope that you can help us to shape"},{"time":612000,"text":"where the technology goes from here. Thank you so much."}]}]}